criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Be willing and able to provide written informed consent/assent for the trial;

          2. Lung cancer patients whose pathological results confirmed is primary non-small cell
             lung cancer, stage III~IV;

          3. Patients received with ICIs treatment, including anti-PD-1 or anti-PD-L1 for at least
             two courses;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients who do not have pathological diagnosis;

          2. Patients who can't finish the follow-up;

          3. The anti-PD-1, anti-PD-L1 therapy was less than two courses;

          4. Patients whose cancer diagnosed with small cell lung cancer.
